Trapper- (6)
- Has the ability to place traps outside any player's house. Any person to visit that player will be weak attacked. Placed traps don't dissapear until they are triggered.
- The traps provide no protection to the player, nor do they attack the player outside whose house the trap was placed.
- The trapper has a cooldown of 2 days(4 phases)
- Placing a trap is an instant action, but is not a visiting action. 
- Respawns in 6 phases.
